title: Dog And Beth On The Hunt S02E04 Fathers and Sons WS DSR x264-[NY
description:
Dog and Beth head up to Sacramento, Calif., to visit their old friend Topo Padilla. Topo runs a family business with his father Greg and son Brandon -- three generations of bounty hunters -- just like the Chapmans. When Dakota and Brandon are tasked with leading the hunt for a dangerous fugitive, it's the challenge of a lifetime. Only one question remains -- can they catch their man, and make their fathers proud?
